cks, using Heated Blade or Hurl Flame in any combination.\n\n**_Heated Blade._** _Melee Attack Roll:_ +10, reach 5 ft. _Hit:_ 13 (2d6 + 6) Slashing damage plus 13 (2d12) Fire damage.\n\n**_Hurl Flame._** _Ranged Attack Roll:_ +8, range 120 ft. _Hit:_ 24 (7d6) Fire damage.\n\n**_Spellcasting._** The efreeti casts one of the following spells, requiring no Material components and using Charisma as the spellcasting ability (spell save DC 16): <br>\n&emsp;**At Will:** _Detect Magic, Elementalism_ <br>\n&emsp;**1/Day Each:** _Gaseous Form, Invisibility, Major Image, Plane Shift, Tongues, Wall of Fire_ (level 7 version)',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-07-05 19:07:01','2026-07-07 18:05:18','[{\"name\": \"Multiattack\", \"desc\": \"Multiattack. The efreeti makes three attacks, using Heated Blade or Hurl Flame in any combination.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 3, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Heated Blade\", \"desc\": \"Heated Blade. Melee Attack Roll: +10, reach 5 ft. Hit: 13 (2d6 + 6) Slashing damage plus 13 (2d12) Fire damage.\", \"attackBonus\": 10, \"damageDice\": \"2d6\", \"damageBonus\": 6, \"damageType\": \"slashing\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Hurl Flame\", \"desc\": \"Hurl Flame. Ranged Attack Roll: +8, range 120 ft. Hit: 24 (7d6) Fire damage.\", \"attackBonus\": 8, \"damageDice\": \"7d6\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"fire\", \"category\": \"ranged\", \"normalRange\": 24, \"longRange\": 24, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Spellcasting\", \"desc\": \"Spell