pe\": \"slashing\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}]',NULL,NULL,NULL),(85,'Gibbering Mouther','Gibbering Mouther','Medium','Aberration','Chaotic Neutral',9,-1,9,52,'7d8 + 21','20 ft., Swim 20 ft.',10,8,16,3,10,6,0,-1,3,-4,0,-2,NULL,NULL,'Prone',NULL,NULL,'Darkvision 60 ft.; Passive Perception 10','None','2',450,2,'**_Aberrant Ground._** The ground in a 10-foot Emanation originating from the mouther is Difficult Terrain.\n\n**_Gibbering._** The mouther babbles incoherently while it doesn\'t have the Incapacitated condition. _Wisdom Saving Throw:_ DC 10, any creature that starts its turn within 20 feet of the mouther while it is babbling. _Failure:_ The target rolls 1d8 to determine what it does during the current turn: <br>\n&emsp;**1–4.** The target does nothing.<br>\n&emsp;**5–6.** The target takes no action or Bonus Action and uses all its movement to move in a random direction.<br>\n&emsp;**7–8.** The target makes a melee attack against a randomly determined creature within its reach or does nothing if it can\'t make such an attack.','**_Bite._** _Melee Attack Roll:_ +2, reach 5 ft. _Hit:_ 7 (2d6) Piercing damage. If the target is a Medium or smaller creature, it has the Prone condition. The target dies if it is reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack. Its body is then absorbed into the mouther, leaving only equipment behind.\n\n**_Blinding Spittle (Recharge 5–6)._** _Dexterity Saving Throw:_ DC 10, each creature in a 10-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point within 30 feet. _Failure:_ 7 (2d6) Radiant damage, and the target has the Blinded condition until the end of the mouther\'s next turn.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-07-05 19:07:01','2026-07-07 18:05:18','[{\"name\": \"Bite\", \"desc\": \"Bite. Melee Attack Roll: +2, reach 5 ft. Hit: 7 (2d6) Piercing damage. If the target is a Medium or smaller creature, it has the Prone condition. The target dies if it is reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack. Its body is then absorbed into the mouther, leaving only equipment behind.\", \"attackBonus\": 2, \"damageDice\": \"2d6\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"piercing\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Blinding Spittle (Recharge 5\\u20136)\", \"desc\": \"Blinding Spittle (Recharge 5\\u20136). Dexterity Saving Throw: DC 10, each creature in a 10-foot-radius Sphere centered on a point within 30 feet. Failure: 7 (2d6) Radiant damage, and the target has the Blinded condition until the end of the mouther\'s next turn.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"2d6\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"radiant\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"dex\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"Dexterity\", \"saveDC\": 10, \"rangeSquares\": 2, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}]','[{\"name\": \"Aberrant Ground\", \"desc\": \"Aberrant Ground. The ground in a 10-foot Emanation originating from the mouther is Difficult Terrain.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Gibbering\", \"desc\": \"Gibbering. The mouther babbles incoherently while it doesn\'t have the Incapacitated condition. Wisdom Saving Throw: DC 10, any creature that starts its turn within 20 feet of the mouther while it is babbling. Failure: The target rolls 1d8 to determine what it does during the current turn: <br>\\n&emsp;1\\u20134. The target does nothing.<br>\\n&emsp;5\\u20136. The target takes no action or Bonus Action and uses all its movement to move in a rand