8:05:18','[{\"name\": \"Abyssal Glaive\", \"desc\": \"Abyssal Glaive. Melee Attack Roll: +6, reach 10 ft. Hit: 10 (1d12 + 4) Slashing damage plus 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage.\", \"attackBonus\": 6, \"damageDice\": \"1d12\", \"damageBonus\": 4, \"damageType\": \"slashing\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Gore (Recharge 5\\u20136)\", \"desc\": \"Gore (Recharge 5\\u20136). Melee Attack Roll: +6, reach 5 ft. Hit: 18 (4d6 + 4) Piercing damage. If the target is a Large or smaller creature and the minotaur moved 10+ feet straight toward it immediately before the hit, the target takes an extra 10 (3d6) Piercing damage and has the Prone condition.\", \"attackBonus\": 6, \"damageDice\": \"4d6\", \"damageBonus\": 4, \"damageType\": \"piercing\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}]',NULL,NULL,NULL),(145,'Mummies','Mummy','Medium','or Small Undead','Lawful Evil',11,-1,9,58,'9d8 + 18','20 ft.',16,8,15,6,12,12,3,-1,2,-2,3,1,NULL,NULL,'Necrotic, Poison; Charmed, Exhaustion, Frightened, Paralyzed, Poisoned','Fire',NULL,'Darkvision 60 ft.; Passive Perception 11','Common plus two other languages','3',700,2,NULL,'**_Multiattack._** The mummy makes two Rotting Fist attacks and uses Dreadful Glare.\n\n**_Rotting Fist._** _Melee Attack Roll:_ +5, reach 5 ft. _Hit:_ 8 (1d10 + 3) Bludgeoning damage plus 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage. If the target is a creature, it is cursed. While cursed, the target can\'t regain Hit Points, its Hit Point maximum doesn\'t return to normal when finishing a Long Rest, and its Hit Point maximum decreases by 10 (3d6) every 24 hours that elapse. A creature dies and turns to dust if reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack.\n\n**_Dreadful Glare._** _Wisdom Saving Throw:_ DC 11, one creature the mummy can see within 60 feet. _Failure:_ The target has the Frightened condition until the end of the mummy\'s next turn. _Success:_ The target is immune to this mummy\'s Dreadful Glare for 24 hours.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'2026-07-05 19:07:01','2026-07-07 18:05:18','[{\"name\": \"Multiattack\", \"desc\": \"Multiattack. The mummy makes two Rotting Fist attacks and uses Dreadful Glare.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 2, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Rotting Fist\", \"desc\": \"Rotting Fist. Melee Attack Roll: +5, reach 5 ft. Hit: 8 (1d10 + 3) Bludgeoning damage plus 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage. If the target is a creature, it is cursed. While cursed, the target can\'t regain Hit Points, its Hit Point maximum doesn\'t return to normal when finishing a Long Rest, and its Hit Point maximum decreases by 10 (3d6) every 24 hours that elapse. A creature dies and turns to dust if reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack.\", \"attackBonus\": 5, \"damageDice\": \"1d10\", \"damageBonus\": 3, \"damageType\": \"bludgeoning\", \"category\": \"melee\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Dreadful Glare\", \"desc\": \"Dreadful Glare. Wisdom Saving Throw: DC 11, one creature the mummy can see within 60 feet. Failure: The target has the Frightened condition until the end of the mummy\'s next turn. Success: The target is immune to this mummy\'s Dreadful Glare for 24 hours.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 0, \"healAmount\": 0}]',NULL,NULL,NULL),(146,'Mummies','Mummy Lord','Medium','or Small Undead (Cleric)','Lawful Evil',17,10,20,187,'25d8 + 75','30 ft.',18,10,17,11,19,16,4,0,3,5,9,3,'History +5, Perception +9, Religion +5',NULL,'Necrotic, Poison; Charmed, Exhaustion, Frightened, Paralyzed, Poisoned','Fire',NULL,'Truesight 60 ft.; Passive Perception 19','Common plus three other languages','15',13000,5,'**_Legendary Resistance (3/Day, or 4/Day in Lair)._** If the mummy fails a saving throw, it can choose to succeed instead.\n\n**_Magic Resistance._** The mummy has Advantage on saving throws against spells and other magical effects.\n\n**_Undead Restoration._** If destroyed, the mummy gains a new body in 24 hours if its heart is intact, reviving with all its Hit Points. The new body appears in an unoccupied space within the mummy\'s lair. The heart is a Tiny object that has AC 17, HP 10, and Immunity to all damage except Fire.','**_Multiattack._** The mummy makes one Rotting Fist or Channel Negative Energy attack, and it uses Dreadful Glare.\n\n**_Rotting Fist._** _Melee Attack Roll:_ +9, reach 5 ft. _Hit:_ 15 (2d10 + 4) Bludgeoning damage plus 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage. If the target is a creature, it is cursed. While cursed, the target can\'t regain Hit Points, it gains no benefit from finishing a Long Rest, and its Hit Point maximum decreases by 10 (3d6) every 24 hours that elapse. A creature dies and turns to dust if reduced to 0 Hit Points by this attack.\n\n**_Channel Negative Energy._** _Ranged Attack Roll:_ +9, range 60 ft. _Hit:_ 25 (6d6 + 4) Necrotic damage.\n\n**_Dreadful Glare._** _Wisdom Saving Throw:_ DC 17, one creature the mummy can see within 60 feet. _Failure:_ 25 (6d6 + 4) Psychic damage, and the target has the Paralyzed condition until the end of the mummy\'s next turn.\n\n**_Spellcasting._** The mummy casts one of the following spells, requiring no Material components and using Wisdom as the spellcasting ability (spell save DC 17, +9 to hit with spell attacks): <br>\n&emsp;**At Will:** _Dispel Magic_, _Thaumaturgy_ <br>\n&emsp;**1/Day Each:** _Animate Dead_, _Harm_, _Insect Plague_ (level 7 version)',NULL,'**_Whirlwind of Sand._** _Trigger:_ The mummy is hit by an attack roll. _Response:_ The mummy adds 2 to its AC against the attack, possibly causing the attack to miss, and the mummy teleports up to 60 feet to an unoccupied space it can see. Each creature of its choice that it can see within 5 feet of its destination space has the Blinded condition until the end of the mummy\'s next turn.','_Legendary Action Uses: 3 (4 in Lair). Immediately after another creature\'s turn, the mummy can expend a use to take one of the following actions. The mummy regains all expended uses at the start of each of its turns._\n\n**_Dread Command._** The mummy casts _Command_ (level 2 version), using the same spellcasting ability as Spellcasting. The mummy can\'t take this action again until the start of its next turn.\n\n**_Glare._** The mummy uses Dreadful Glare. The mummy can\'t take this action again until the start of its next turn.\n\n**_Necrotic Strike._** The mummy makes one Rotting Fist or Channel Negative Energy attack.','2026-07-05 19:07:01','2026-07-07 18:05:18','[{\"name\": \"Multiattack\", \"desc\": \"Multiattack. The mummy makes one Rotting Fist or Channel Negative Energy attack, and it uses Dreadful Glare.\", \"attackBonus\": 0, \"damageDice\": \"\", \"damageBonus\": 0, \"damageType\": \"\", \"category\": \"\", \"normalRange\": 0, \"longRange\": 0, \"saveAbility\": \"\", \"saveAbilityLabel\": \"\", \"saveDC\": 0, \"rangeSquares\": 0, \"multiattackCount\": 1, \"healAmount\": 0}, {\"name\": \"Rotting Fist\", \"desc\": \"Rotting Fist. Melee Attack Roll: +9, reach 5 ft. Hit: 15 (2d10 + 4) Bludgeoning damage plus 10 (3d6) Necrotic damage. If the target is a creature, it is cursed. While cursed, the target can\'t regain Hit Points, it gains no benefit from finishing a Long Res